          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Democracy Dollars Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes the Democracy Fund Commission to operate a Democracy Dollars Program under which individuals eligible to vote may direct payments to (1) candidates for federal office who meet specified donor thresholds, or (2) eligible political committees.</p>]]></text>
